text: Svitlana Zelepukina (born 16 August 1980) is a Ukrainian gymnast. She competed in six events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Ukraine Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Kropyvnytskyi
